
Action Plan (TODO file)
-----------------------

1. Test more and refine basic transient analysis with fixed time step

2. Add simulation examples in documentation

3. Add sparse matrix support and optimize inner loops to improve
   speed: modify nodal.py to use pytrilinos
   (http://trilinos.sandia.gov/packages/pytrilinos/) to access the KLU
   sparse matrix library
   (http://www.cise.ufl.edu/research/sparse/klu/). Inner loop
   functions (``set_*`` in ``nodal.py``) will be re-implemented using
   cython (http://cython.org/).

4. Add support for convolution of freq-defined elements

Other tasks to be done at some time:

* Improve convergence control in Newton method

* Implement extrinsic model for MOS trasistors using an approach
  similar to the BJT implementation.

* Add "+" notation for multiple lines in parser 



